following functionalities are affected in authentication related bugs:-
1.registration page
2.login page
3.forgot password
4.change password / password reset
5.confirm email address
6.OAUTH
7.authenticated action bypass
8.multifactor authentication like:-
    1.otp
    2.email me the code
    3.satillite generator
    4.sms / call
    5.backup codes
9.cookie based authentication vulnerabilities
10.insecure transmission of credentials
11.default credentials
12.openredirect in oauth / authentication after process
13.vulnerable remember password
14.weak password policy
15.weak security question answer
16.username enumeration
17.E-mail enumeration
18.SAML configuration
19.OpenID connect
20.jwt / json web token
21.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
attacking username / username enumeration :
  usernames should be stored case insensitively  and  be  UNIQUE 
  
  
attacking password block enumeration:-
  disable cut ,copy and paste
  password hints which lack sufficient entropy
  password policy should be strong
  
